        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued November 1 at 6:23PM CDT until November 1 at 7:00PM CDT by NWS Houston/Galveston TX</headline>
        <description>SVRHGX

The National Weather Service in League City has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Central Matagorda County in southeastern Texas...

* Until 700 PM CDT.

* At 623 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Markham, or 7
miles west of Bay City, moving southeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

* Locations impacted include...
Bay City, South Texas Nuclear Plant, Markham, and Wadsworth.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
